e_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217876}, {"id": 254984, "content": "用一本的分数上了三本", "image": null, "praise_count": 254, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163418}, {"id": 255240, "content": "全国5亿多人有家庭医生。还未超过一半，仍需努力吹。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217880}, {"id": 254985, "content": "更多的校园杀人事件", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070127}, {"id": 255241, "content": "去年冬天帝都各种重度污染，今年冬天天蓝气清。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217851}, {"id": 255242, "content": "红色黄色蓝色是最鲜艳的色彩，但是对于有些人可能是无限的黑暗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217886}, {"id": 255243, "content": "对谁是社会主义接班人这一问题有了新的思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217861}, {"id": 255244, "content": "现实荒诞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217890}, {"id": 255245, "content": "对人类对压迫强度的容忍有了新的认识", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217893}, {"id": 255246, "content": "抬头看到的标语以为坐上了时间飞船", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217872}, {"id": 255247, "content": "他说：我拿着助学金出国旅游怎么了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217904}, {"id": 255248, "content": "学历不重要\n对不起，我们只要985 211???", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217874}, {"id": 255249, "content": "十二月的北京竟然几乎没有雾霾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 47221}, {"id": 254994, "content": "我竟然还活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 361, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910665}, {"id": 255250, "content": "最大的魔幻现实主义就是不让人说魔幻现实主义??‍♂️", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188926}, {"id": 255251, "content": "楚门的世界一直就在。每个人都是楚门", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411579}, {"id": 254